collection.description:
This is Deadheads. The reanimated adventures of dead souls owned by living fans.

We interweave story-telling and web3 technology to disrupt the existing fan experience, [watch DeadHeads Animated Series Here](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCLAbt0FzUCe5BRAtMM40Ikg)

Our underworld is swarming with fresh, corruptible, tradeable souls. With the IP rights in your pocket, youâ€™ll get the chance to put your characters in the show or bring them to life in weird and disturbing ways. 

[Visit Our DApp](https://app.deadheads.io)

By buying the NFT of an original Deadhead, you can give them the chance to appear on the show, make and sell merch, or simply turn them into a 3D model to darken the vibe of your mantlepiece.
